political voice to the countrys 28 million blacks south africas 
5 million whites control the government and economy 
at a dinner speech at a glitzy toronto hotel mandela told a 
mostly white audience that whites are not the enemy in the fight 
against apartheid 
we are facing a common front not against whites but against 
racial oppression he said to resounding applause 
