houphouetboigny of ivory coast and mobutu sese seko of zaire are 
not attending the summit both recently made concessions to 
opposition groups by proposing multiparty systems mobutu has been 
beset by calls for an international inquiry into an alleged 
massacre of scores of university students by security forces 
