thirtyeight republicans said they would vote yes and three are 
undecided 
that the survey found so many democrats on the fence so close to 
a vote illustrates the political difficulty of the issue which 
sen bob dole rkan has quipped would make a good 30second 
campaign spot 
but rep richard durbin dill who was undecided last week 
said he found in a visit to his home district that the issue wasnt 
pressing with constituents he said hes now leaning against the 
amendment 
