arrangement under it ltv agreed to make up any benefits lost to 
retirees that are not covered by the federal pension insurance 
program 
the pbgc contended such arrangements are abusive and the agency 
ordered ltv to reassume responsibility for the pension plans when 
ltv refused the agency sought to enforce its order in federal 
court 
