manakh stock exchange under the weight of 94 billion in postdated 
checks oman also has a fledgling stock exchange 
behzad said the gcc stock exchanges were cooperating to create a 
strong capital market in the wealthy gulf states which sit on 
twothirds of the worlds proven oil reserves 
behzad said that the first year saw 776 million shares traded 
and worth the equivalent of about 788 million through 3160 
transactions transfer of ownership involved 11 million shares 
worth 81 million through 177 transactions 
a total of 29 companies are so far listed on the exchange and 
abc will be the 30th 
