and associates a retail consulting firm in new york you try to 
identify unprofitable operations and wipe them out that 
doesnt come free 
ames filed for protection from its creditors under chapter 11 of 
the us bankruptcy code on april 25 
a hearing is scheduled thursday in us bankruptcy court in new 
york on ames plan to close the stores which employ about 17500 
full and parttime employees most of the stores being closed are 
